{"tid":1420514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警有公共關係科 義士現場都應該要有","createTime":"2019-08-06T04:53:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T15:45:57.000Z","uid":258192,"like":40,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"25b85e7db056494e82ce36b09e5efc34f5da5aa5","tid":1420514,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:53:02.000Z","msg":"黑警個公共關係科係禁講「我唔知/要問現場指揮官/I am working ar」其實正常dse中/英文說話有返5*or above都應該勁過警犬 <span style=\"color: red;\">要公共關係做得好過佢真係易過食生菜</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">所以義士都應該要有返個公共關係科</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">職責</span><br />\n貼近記者企前面<br />\n現場解答記者問題<br />\n如記者需要 提供小量水/食物/急救用品<br />\n提示記者警犬過度使用武力位置 (令警犬無法使用武力)<br />\n解話 幫義士消毒<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">能力</span><br />\n口才要勁<br />\n中/英說話能力高超英文(做到同英文native差唔多就最好)<br />\n腦筋急轉彎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">服裝</span><br />\n一部go pro/small camera掛心口 長期record 最好可以upload上cloud(比警犬拉示威可以有證據証明無參與)<br />\n黑衫 背脊好似running man點公共關係科，但唔好話係咩聯絡人禁樣會比人charge你同示威者有聯繫<br />\n唔好攞任何野除左頭盔同口罩(因爲要貼近記者係前排)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想問法律巴 如果同示威無關 企係街會唔會比人拉 告唔告得入</span></span>"},{"pid":"fde387225b0884bf8fe45abb19a7e4ef53ba7636","tid":1420514,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:53:42.000Z","msg":"認同請分享 好人一生平安"},{"pid":"df52f9a47f6f613fdaa799fc9d07f9b7e03b0b1c","tid":1420514,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:57:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"79a4d2fe3647bdb2fa3358c79d4d9c28eb5f67d3","tid":1420514,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:58:05.000Z","msg":"十連推"},{"pid":"cdd2f01132dddcdcf5f5183a3ec417a3b7d23d54","tid":1420514,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:58:15.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"0311d7e2c901e463ed413df011045219b6771c33","tid":1420514,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s